universe of origin : an anime-world catalogued into UD0
seal               : An over-the-top action anime where a school uniform can level a city block and a sailor suit talks back. Ryuko Matoi storms Honnouji Academy carrying half of a giant scissor-blade, hunting her father's killer — and finds that the source of every power here, and the threat to the whole world, is a single thread: the Life Fiber, woven into the clothes everyone wears. Studio Trigger's debut, loud on purpose, and smarter than it lets on.
